 <!-- creating store -->
- npm i react-redux and @reduxjs/toolkit
- create new folder for redux files
- create redux store using configureStore method of toolkit and store it in variable and export the store
- create reducer in store

<!-- creating slice -->
- create slice for counter
- create new file counterSlice and create new slice using createSlice method[name, initial state->value, reducers:{functions}]
- extract the actions from slice using sliceName.actions method
- export sliceName.reducer

- wrap the App comp. inside store provider

<!-- using in compts -->
- import useDispatch and useSelector from react-redux
- const dispatch = useDispatch..... calling dispatcher
- select state value from store using useSelector and store in const var.
- use const var.

